The '''''European Business Law Review''''' ({{ISSN|0959-6941}}) is a [[law review|law journal]] covering [[commercial law|business law]], broadly defined and including both [[European Union]] law and the laws of the Member States and other European countries. It is published by [[Wolters Kluwer|Kluwer Law International]].

